question_id: Tampilkan staf yang jumlah transaksi pembayarannya lebih sedikit daripada rata-rata jumlah transaksi per staf; sertakan nama depan, nama belakang, dan jumlah transaksinya.
sql_query:
SELECT
    a.first_name AS nama_depan,
    a.last_name AS nama_belakang,
    COUNT(r.rental_id) AS jumlah_transaksi
FROM
    staff a
JOIN
    rental r ON a.staff_id = r.staff_id
GROUP BY
    a.staff_id, a.first_name, a.last_name
HAVING
    COUNT(r.rental_id) < (SELECT AVG(rental_id) FROM staff)
raw_response:
```sql

    a.first_name AS nama_depan,
    a.last_name AS nama_belakang,
    COUNT(r.rental_id) AS jumlah_transaksi

    rental r ON a.staff_id = r.staff_id
GROUP BY

HAVING
```
